parameters.name: model_id
parameters.label: model_id
parameters.help: Destination id for this model; auto-generated if not specified.

parameters.name: training_frame
parameters.label: training_frame
parameters.help: Id of the training data frame.

parameters.name: validation_frame
parameters.label: validation_frame
parameters.help: Id of the validation data frame.

parameters.name: blending_frame
parameters.label: blending_frame
parameters.help: Frame used to compute the predictions that serve as the training frame for the metalearner (triggers blending mode if provided)

parameters.name: base_models
parameters.label: base_models
parameters.help: List of models or grids (or their ids) to ensemble/stack together. Grids are expanded to individual models. If not using blending frame, then models must have been cross-validated using nfolds > 1, and folds must be identical across models.

parameters.name: metalearner_algorithm
parameters.label: metalearner_algorithm
parameters.help: Type of algorithm to use as the metalearner. Options include 'AUTO' (GLM with non negative weights; if validation_frame is present, a lambda search is performed), 'deeplearning' (Deep Learning with default parameters), 'drf' (Random Forest with default parameters), 'gbm' (GBM with default parameters), 'glm' (GLM with default parameters), 'naivebayes' (NaiveBayes with default parameters), or 'xgboost' (if available, XGBoost with default parameters).

parameters.name: metalearner_nfolds
parameters.label: metalearner_nfolds
parameters.help: Number of folds for K-fold cross-validation of the metalearner algorithm (0 to disable or >= 2).

parameters.name: metalearner_fold_assignment
parameters.label: metalearner_fold_assignment
parameters.help: Cross-validation fold assignment scheme for metalearner cross-validation.  Defaults to AUTO (which is currently set to Random). The 'Stratified' option will stratify the folds based on the response variable, for classification problems.

parameters.name: metalearner_fold_column
parameters.label: metalearner_fold_column
parameters.help: Column with cross-validation fold index assignment per observation for cross-validation of the metalearner.

parameters.name: seed
parameters.label: seed
parameters.help: Seed for random numbers; passed through to the metalearner algorithm. Defaults to -1 (time-based random number)

parameters.name: score_training_samples
parameters.label: score_training_samples
parameters.help: Specify the number of training set samples for scoring. The value must be >= 0. To use all training samples, enter 0.

parameters.name: keep_levelone_frame
parameters.label: keep_levelone_frame
parameters.help: Keep level one frame used for metalearner training.

parameters.name: export_checkpoints_dir
parameters.label: export_checkpoints_dir
parameters.help: Automatically export generated models to this directory.
